 />\nsorry very much"},{"pid":"e77bfbd0863b18f07d097c8ff06a0c9c7fa00ea5","tid":381970,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T17:47:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>The claim by the three respondents that they were going to &ldquo;recapture the Civic Square&rdquo; by way of the zero-violence principle of &ldquo;peace, rationality and non-violence&rdquo; was nothing but empty talk, something to which they paid lip service and a slogan by which they deluded themselves and others.</blockquote><br />\n重以為睇緊環球時報"},{"pid":"bc8dad1a974a966f7bd637f4826fa429b9f42c97","tid":381970,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T17:52:55.000Z","msg":"原來香港法律已經衰到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}